modName: Daedric bikini type M2 M3 M4 CBBE UNP - DELETED
summary: Daedric bikini, 34 versions in chest, temperable, for CBBE 3.4f and UNP 1.2. Stats like daedric armor.
descriptionHtml:
[size=6][font=Arial][b][color=#fff2cc]Description[/color][/b][/font]
[size=3]Mod contains daedric bikini 34 color versions (3 types).
[size=3]Items are in chest in Riverwood near river. Items are temperable, [size=6][size=3] armor stats like stats of daedric armor[/size][/size].
[size=6][size=3] name "Daedric bikini M2", [size=6][size=3][size=3][size=6][size=3]"Daedric bikini M3",[/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size] "Daedric bikini M4 ".[color=#ffd966][size=4] [b]File with M4 version available in optional[/b][/size][/color][color=#ffe599], however design of it looks weird. Look carefully at screenshots to be sure if you need it.[/color]
Color versions: black (gems: red, yellow, blue, purple, green), steel[size=3] (gems: red, blue, purple, green), [size=3]gold[size=3] (gems: red, blue, purple, green), [size=3][size=3][size=3]copper[size=3] (gems: red, blue, purple, green)[/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size]. 3 types of bikini: M2 and M3 and M4. M4 type has animated fire shaders - available in optional.
Mod was made for CBBE 3.4f (latest) and UNP 1.2 (latest) supports weight slider.
Sandals for it are here [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90141]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90141[/url]
Necklace and circlet from screens are here [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86647]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86647[/url]
Thank you for your endorsments and screens!
PS. 1st screen - M3, 2nd - M4, 3rd- M2
PS2. Why type M? M as mermaid - first thought when I looked at design of top.
PS3. File with M4 version available in "optional files" only. As I understood - it is too strange concept, so people don't like it too much. If you don't like to see animated fire shaders on the bikini - install version 1.10-1.11.

Permissions:
You can make anything what you want while it is non-commercial destribution
and you give me credits as original mod author and link to original
page.
I don't give permission to upload it in steam.[/size][/size]
